member_experience_collection.title: Account Executive
member_experience_collection.description:
Striving to be the best partner for her clients, Belinda works daily to ensure that her clients are making the most of the value solutions that Sogeti offers. In a Hunter/Farmer position, Belinda not only prospects locally to bring in new clients, but also works to ensure delivery excellence in her named accounts. Sogeti is able to deliver services ranging from Professional Services, Consulting Services, Rightshore Services, Project (deliverable based) Services, and Managed Services.

Some of the key areas of focus include:

• Software Development and Integration
• Quality Assurance and Managed Testing
• Project Management and Agile Coaching/Transformation
• Business Intelligence/Business Consulting
• Applications Management
• Enterprise Architecture and Digital Transformation


Learn more about us and our technology service offerings at http://us.sogeti.com/

member_experience_collection.title: Account Manager
member_experience_collection.description:
As an Account Manager at Apex I was privileged to work with some of the sharpest companies in Phoenix. I spent my time investing in my clients to best understand what type of candidates we could provide them that will add the most value to their team. The candidates that were placed through Apex at my client sites ranged from short term contractors to permanent candidates.

"Apex Systems is a leading provider of technical and professional staffing solutions to Fortune 1000 and mid-sized clients across North America. With a core focus on Information Technology, Business Applications, Accounting & Finance, Legal, Telecommunications, and Engineering, and a proven recruiting model, Apex Systems has become one of the most in-demand staffing companies around for providing short-term, long-term, and temp-to-perm staffing solutions.

Whether it’s supplementing existing staff during peak periods in production or hiring a permanent employee through the temporary process, Apex Systems is the answer. Our ultimate goal is to save our clients time and money while increasing efficiency, productivity, and bottom-line profit.

Apex Systems, Inc. is currently the 8th largest staffing firm in the United states and is in the top 15 fastest growing."

member_experience_collection.title: Technical Recruiter
member_experience_collection.description: As a Technical Recruiter at Apex, I helped to identify and screen the top local talent to pass on to our clients. I worked hand in hand with the Account Managers to find candidates that would love the work environment and bring success to their team.

In a Hunter/Farmer position, Belinda not only prospects locally to bring in new clients, but also works to ensure delivery excellence in her named accounts.  Sogeti is able to deliver services ranging from Professional Services, Consulting Services, Rightshore Services, Project (deliverable based) Services, and Managed Services.

Some of the key areas of focus include:

• Software Development and Integration
• Quality Assurance and Managed Testing
• Project Management and Agile Coaching/Transformation
• Business Intelligence/Business Consulting
• Applications Management
• Enterprise Architecture and Digital Transformation


Learn more about us and our technology service offerings at http://us.sogeti.com/

member_experience_collection.title: Account Manager
member_experience_collection.description:
As an Account Manager at Apex I was privileged to work with some of the sharpest companies in Phoenix.  I spent my time investing in my clients to best understand what type of candidates we could provide them that will add the most value to their team.  The candidates that were placed through Apex at my client sites ranged from short term contractors to permanent candidates.

"Apex Systems is a leading provider of technical and professional staffing solutions to Fortune 1000 and mid-sized clients across North America. With a core focus on Information Technology, Business Applications, Accounting & Finance, Legal, Telecommunications, and Engineering, and a proven recruiting model, Apex Systems has become one of the most in-demand staffing companies around for providing short-term, long-term, and temp-to-perm staffing solutions.

Whether it’s supplementing existing staff during peak periods in production or hiring a permanent employee through the temporary process, Apex Systems is the answer. Our ultimate goal is to save our clients time and money while increasing efficiency, productivity, and bottom-line profit.

Apex Systems, Inc. is currently the 8th largest staffing firm in the United states and is in the top 15 fastest growing."
